    <fr:anchor>745</fr:anchor>
    <fr:addr type="user">FA-0031</fr:addr>
    <fr:route>FA-0031.xml</fr:route>
    <fr:title text="Orthogonal complement">Orthogonal complement</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
    <fr:date>
      <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
      <fr:month>5</fr:month>
      <fr:day>26</fr:day>
    </fr:date>
    <fr:authors>
      <fr:author>Long Nguyen</fr:author>
    </fr:authors>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> be a subset of a <fr:link type="local" href="FA-0030.xml" addr="FA-0030" title="Hilbert Space">Hilbert space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex>. The orthogonal complement of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex>, denoted <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S^\perp ]]></fr:tex>, is the set of all vectors in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex> that are orthogonal to every vector in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>Formally, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S^\perp  = \{y \in  H : \langle  x, y \rangle  = 0 \text { for all } x \in  S\}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>Some important properties:</fr:p>
    <fr:ul><fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S^\perp ]]></fr:tex> is a closed subspace of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(S^\perp )^\perp  = \overline {\text {span}(S)}]]></fr:tex>, where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {\text {span}(S)}]]></fr:tex> is the <fr:link type="local" href="FA-0040.xml" addr="FA-0040" title="Closed linear span">closed linear span</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H = \overline {\text {span}(S)} \oplus  S^\perp ]]></fr:tex></fr:li>, where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\oplus ]]></fr:tex> represents the <fr:link type="local" href="FA-0041.xml" addr="FA-0041" title="Direct sum">direct sum</fr:link> of subspaces</fr:ul>
  </fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:backmatter>
    <fr:tree toc="false" numbered="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" expanded="true" root="false" xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml">
